    "description": "Reconnect-telemetry summary line on the OBD2 diagnostics card (#2905). attempts is the per-attempt-timeline row count; successes the attempts that re-established a link; transitions the session-state-transition marker count; disconnects the Obd2DisconnectedException (typed drop) count.",
